 if you are feeling helpless and flat, just remember, I&rsquo;m here for you. I will always be here for you. </p>          <p>Sincerely,<br>            Pernice DeMension, M.D.</p></td>      </tr>      <tr>        <td width="466" colspan="4">&nbsp;</td>      </tr>      <tr>        <td colspan="4">&nbsp;</td>      </tr>    </table>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td><img src="images/bottom_line.gif" width="799" height="26"></td>  </tr></table></body></html>